<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
{% include '_partials/seo' with { legacyTemplate: 'contact.html' } %}
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"><link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Saira:ital,wght@0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;1,600;1,700;1,800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="kikers.css?v=20260713-craftcms3">
</head>
<body id="top">

{% include '_partials/site-header' with { navActive: 'visit', ctaLabel: 'Call Us', ctaHref: 'phone', drawerCtaLabel: 'Call ' ~ siteSettings.phoneNumber } %}

<nav class="crumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><div class="wrap"><a href="index.html">Home</a><span class="sep">›</span><span>Contact &amp; Visit</span></div></nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero compact">
  <div class="hero-photo ph ph--dark"><div class="ph-tag"><span class="kk">📷 HERO BACKGROUND</span><span class="d">Storefront / gate with the Kiker's sign — daylight, recognizable on arrival.</span></div></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="h-tags"><span class="eyebrow on-ink">Visit the Yard</span><span class="chiplet">Pensacola, FL</span><span class="ecobadge on-ink">♻ Recycled responsibly</span></div>
    <h1>Come see us <em>at the yard.</em></h1>
    <p class="lede">Selling a vehicle or pulling your own parts — here's everything you need to find us, reach us, and know before you come.</p>
    <div class="cta-row"><a class="btn btn--amber btn--lg" href="tel:{{ siteSettings.phoneNumber|replace({"-": ""}) }}"><span class="ic">📞</span>Call {{ siteSettings.phoneNumber }}</a><a class="btn btn--outline-light btn--lg" href="#directions"><span class="ic">📍</span>Get Directions</a></div>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="hazard"></div>

<!-- METHODS -->
<section class="sec">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head center"><span class="eyebrow">How to Reach Us</span><h2 style="font-style:italic">The fastest ways to get an answer</h2><p>Selling a car? Calling is quickest — we move fast. Pulling parts? Come on by during hours.</p></div>
    <div class="methods">
      <div class="mcard"><div class="ic">📞</div><h3>Call the yard</h3><p>The quickest way to get a cash offer or ask about a vehicle or part.</p><span class="big">{{ siteSettings.phoneNumber }}</span><a class="btn btn--filled btn--block" href="tel:{{ siteSettings.phoneNumber|replace({"-": ""}) }}"><span class="ic">📞</span>Call Now</a></div>
      <div class="mcard"><div class="ic">⚡</div><h3>Get a cash offer</h3><p>Selling a car, truck, or SUV? Send a few details and we'll call or text you right back.</p><a class="btn btn--ink btn--block" href="sell-your-vehicle.html" style="margin-top:auto"><span class="ic">→</span>Sell Your Vehicle</a></div>
      <div class="mcard"><div class="ic">📍</div><h3>Get directions</h3><p>Open Mon-Fri, 9 AM to 4:30 PM; Sat, 8 AM to 2 PM. Pull up the map and head our way.</p><a class="btn btn--outline btn--block" href="#directions" style="margin-top:auto"><span class="ic">→</span>Directions</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- LOCATION + HOURS -->
<section class="sec" id="directions" style="background:var(--surface-3)">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head"><span class="eyebrow">Location &amp; Hours</span><h2 style="font-style:italic">Find the yard</h2></div>
    <div class="loc-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="map"><iframe title="Map to Kiker's U-Pull-It" src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=3010%20W%20Fairfield%20Dr%2C%20Pensacola%2C%20FL%2032505&output=embed" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe></div>
        <div class="addr-row"><div class="a1">{{ siteSettings.streetAddress }}</div><a class="a2" href="tel:{{ siteSettings.phoneNumber|replace({"-": ""}) }}">{{ siteSettings.phoneNumber }}</a>
          <div style="margin-top:16px;display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap"><a class="btn btn--ink" href="{{ siteSettings.directionsUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="ic">📍</span>Get Directions</a><a class="btn btn--outline" href="tel:{{ siteSettings.phoneNumber|replace({"-": ""}) }}">Call the Yard</a></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hours">
        <h3>Hours</h3>
        <div style="margin-bottom:14px;font-size:13px"><span class="dot" style="display:inline-block;margin-right:6px"></span><b id="statusText">Hours today</b></div>
        <table class="htable" id="htable">
          <tr data-d="1"><td class="day">Monday</td><td class="hrs">9:00 AM – 4:30 PM</td></tr>
          <tr data-d="2"><td class="day">Tuesday</td><td class="hrs">9:00 AM – 4:30 PM</td></tr>
          <tr data-d="3"><td class="day">Wednesday</td><td class="hrs">9:00 AM – 4:30 PM</td></tr>
          <tr data-d="4"><td class="day">Thursday</td><td class="hrs">9:00 AM – 4:30 PM</td></tr>
          <tr data-d="5"><td class="day">Friday</td><td class="hrs">9:00 AM – 4:30 PM</td></tr>
          <tr data-d="6"><td class="day">Saturday</td><td class="hrs">8:00 AM – 2:00 PM</td></tr>
          <tr data-d="0"><td class="day">Sunday</td><td class="hrs">Closed</td></tr>
        </table>
        <div class="last">Last admission 30 minutes before close.</div>
        <div class="pays"><span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-2);font-weight:600;margin-right:4px">We accept:</span><span class="pc">VISA</span><span class="pc">MC</span><span class="pc">AMEX</span><span class="pc">DISC</span><span class="pc">CASH</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TWO PATHS -->
<section class="sec">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head center"><span class="eyebrow">First Time Here?</span><h2 style="font-style:italic">What brings you in?</h2></div>
    <div class="paths">
      <div class="path">
        <div class="ph ph--16x9"><div class="ph-in"><span class="ph-cam">📷</span><span class="ph-kick">PHOTO — SELLING</span><span class="ph-desc">A vehicle on the flatbed, or a seller at the counter.</span></div></div>
        <div class="pbody"><div class="ic">💵</div><h3>Selling a vehicle</h3><p>You don't even have to come in — we'll come to you.</p>
          <ul><li><span class="c">✓</span> Call or send your vehicle details for a cash offer</li><li><span class="c">✓</span> We schedule a same-day or convenient pickup</li><li><span class="c">✓</span> Free towing, paperwork handled, cash in hand</li></ul>
          <a class="btn btn--filled btn--block" href="sell-your-vehicle.html" style="margin-top:auto"><span class="ic">⚡</span>Get a Cash Offer</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="path">
        <div class="ph ph--16x9"><div class="ph-in"><span class="ph-cam">📷</span><span class="ph-kick">PHOTO — PULLING PARTS</span><span class="ph-desc">A customer pulling a part in an organized row.</span></div></div>
        <div class="pbody"><div class="ic">🔧</div><h3>Pulling your own parts</h3><p>It's self-serve — come in during hours, bring your tools, and pull what you need.</p>
          <ul><li><span class="c">✓</span> Bring your own tools and gloves</li><li><span class="c">✓</span> Find your vehicle by section and row</li><li><span class="c">✓</span> Pay for what you pull at the counter</li></ul>
          <a class="btn btn--ink btn--block" href="u-pull-parts.html" style="margin-top:auto"><span class="ic">→</span>Search Inventory</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- YARD RULES -->
<section class="sec" style="background:var(--surface-3)">
  <div class="wrap"><div class="split2 top">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">Before You Come</span>
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(23px,3vw,31px);margin:8px 0 6px;font-style:italic">Yard rules &amp; safety</h2>
      <p class="lead-p">A working salvage yard has real hazards. A few simple rules keep everybody safe — and keep your visit quick.</p>
    </div>
    <ul class="policies" style="border:none;padding:0;margin:0"><div style="display:grid;gap:14px;font-size:15px">
      <li>🧰 <span><b>Bring your own tools and gloves.</b> It's self-serve — we don't pull parts for you.</span></li>
      <li>👟 <span><b>Closed-toe shoes required.</b> Heavy steel and sharp metal are everywhere.</span></li>
      <li>🔞 <span><b>16 and up on the yard.</b> For everyone's safety.</span></li>
      <li>⚠️ <span><b>Watch for hazards.</b> Heavy parts, sharp edges, fluids — and look out for the person next to you.</span></li>
      <li>🏷️ <span><b>Parts are priced at the counter.</b> Pull what you need, pay on your way out.</span></li>
    </div></ul>
  </div></div>
</section>

<!-- MESSAGE FORM -->
<section class="sec" id="message">
  <div class="wrap"><div class="split2 top">
    <div class="info">
      <span class="eyebrow">Send a Message</span>
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(23px,3vw,31px);margin:8px 0 10px;font-style:italic">Have a question?</h2>
      <p class="lead-p">Use the form and we'll get back to you. For a cash offer on a vehicle, calling is faster.</p>
      <div class="qline"><span class="ic">📞</span><span><b><a href="tel:{{ siteSettings.phoneNumber|replace({"-": ""}) }}">{{ siteSettings.phoneNumber }}</a></b><span class="s">Call - Mon-Fri, 9 AM to 4:30 PM; Sat, 8 AM to 2 PM</span></span></div>
      <div class="qline"><span class="ic">✉️</span><span><b>sales@kikersautoparts.com</b><span class="s">Email the yard</span></span></div>
      <div class="qline" style="border-bottom:none"><span class="ic">💬</span><span><b>Facebook &amp; Instagram</b><span class="s">@kikersupullit — add the real links</span></span></div>
    </div>
    <form class="form-card" onsubmit="return submitMsg(event)">
      <div class="grid2" style="margin-bottom:16px"><div class="field"><label>Name</label><input placeholder="First &amp; last" required></div><div class="field"><label>Phone</label><input type="tel" placeholder="(850) 000-0000" required></div></div>
      <div class="field" style="margin-bottom:16px"><label>Email (optional)</label><input type="email" placeholder="you@email.com"></div>
      <div class="field" style="margin-bottom:16px"><label>What can we help with?</label><select required><option value="" selected disabled>Select…</option><option>Selling a vehicle</option><option>Finding a part</option><option>Inventory question</option><option>Something else</option></select></div>
      <div class="field" style="margin-bottom:18px"><label>Message</label><textarea placeholder="Tell us a bit more…"></textarea></div>
      <button class="btn btn--filled btn--block btn--lg" type="submit"><span class="ic">→</span>Send Message</button>
      <div class="disclaim">We'll reply during business hours. For a fast cash offer, call {{ siteSettings.phoneNumber }}.</div>
    </form>
  </div></div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="sec" style="background:var(--surface-3)">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head center"><span class="eyebrow">Good to Know</span><h2 style="font-style:italic">Visiting Kiker's: FAQ</h2></div>
    <div class="faq">
      <details open><summary>What are your hours? <span class="pm">+</span></summary><div class="ans">We're open <b>Monday through Friday, 9 AM to 4:30 PM, and Saturday, 8 AM to 2 PM</b>, and closed Sunday. Last admission to the yard is 30 minutes before close.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Do I need an appointment? <span class="pm">+</span></summary><div class="ans">No. For parts, just come in during hours. If you're <b>selling a vehicle</b>, call ahead at {{ siteSettings.phoneNumber }} so we can schedule a fast pickup.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Do I need my own tools to pull parts? <span class="pm">+</span></summary><div class="ans">Yes — it's a <b>self-serve yard</b>. Bring your own tools and gloves and pull the parts you need. Parts are priced at the counter.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Is there an age requirement to enter the yard? <span class="pm">+</span></summary><div class="ans">Yes. You must be <b>16 or older</b> to go out on the yard, and closed-toe shoes are required.</div></details>
      <details><summary>What forms of payment do you accept? <span class="pm">+</span></summary><div class="ans">We accept <b>Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Discover, and cash</b>.</div></details>
      <details><summary>How do I sell my vehicle to you? <span class="pm">+</span></summary><div class="ans">Call <b>{{ siteSettings.phoneNumber }}</b> or use our <a href="sell-your-vehicle.html">Sell Your Vehicle</a> page. We give a fair cash offer, tow it free, handle the paperwork, and pay you — often the same day.</div></details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="race-rule"></div>
<section class="finalcta"><div class="wrap">
  <div><h2>Come on by — or let us come to you.</h2><p>Open Mon-Fri, 9 AM to 4:30 PM; Sat, 8 AM to 2 PM. Selling a vehicle? We'll handle the rest.</p></div>
  <div class="grp"><a class="btn btn--amber btn--lg" href="tel:{{ siteSettings.phoneNumber|replace({"-": ""}) }}"><span class="ic">📞</span>Call {{ siteSettings.phoneNumber }}</a><a class="btn btn--outline-light btn--lg" href="sell-your-vehicle.html">Get a Cash Offer</a></div>
</div></section>

{% include '_partials/site-footer' %}

